\v 1  \w The|strong="H3068"\w* \nd \+w Lord|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* \w spoke|strong="H1697"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w me|strong="H1961"\w*. \w He|strong="H3068"\w* \w said|strong="H1697"\w*:  
